Instagram Gallery
--------------------------

Tool to to view instagram public profile photos

Qt > 5.4.0
Ubuntu 14.04

-------------------------
Usage:

Gallery window:
1. Type instagram progile name into
2. Click "Load"
3. To load next publications, click "Load more" at the bottom of view
4. DoubleClick on thumbnail to show in full resolution

Details window:
1. DoubleClick to zoom in/out
2. Press left mouse button to pan image while zoomed
3. Press right mouse button to center view

